    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">Software</a> * <a href=\"/Utilities\" title=\"Utilities\">Utilities</a> * UCI2WB</b>\n</p><p><b>UCI2WB</b>,<br />\nwas originally a <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">protocol</a> adapter by <a href=\"/Roland_Pfister\" title=\"Roland Pfister\">Roland Pfister</a> to run <a href=\"/Category:UCI\" title=\"Category:UCI\">UCI Engines</a> under <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a>. As no longer maintained closed source, some flaws and limitations emerged after a few years, and UCI2WB was replaced in 2004 by <a href=\"/Fabien_Letouzey\" title=\"Fabien Letouzey\">Fabien Letouzey's</a> <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \n<span id=\"USI2WB\"></span>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#USI2WB_.2F_UCI2WB\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">USI2WB / UCI2WB</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Engines\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Engines</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#GUIs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">GUIs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Pfister\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Pfister</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Muller\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Muller</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"USI2WB_.2F_UCI2WB\">USI2WB / UCI2WB</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: USI2WB / UCI2WB\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>In about 2009, <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a> started to develop an <b>USI2WB</b> adapter to support <a href=\"/Shogi\" title=\"Shogi\">Shogi</a> engines using the <a href=\"/USI\" title=\"USI\">USI</a> protocol <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. USI2WB was then generalized to became a new UCI2WB cross <a href=\"/Games#ChessVariants\" title=\"Games\">variant</a> protocol adapter for <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> dialect engines (UCI, USI, UCCI, UCI-Cyclone, Arena960) to play with <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> or <a href=\"/XBoard\" title=\"XBoard\">XBoard</a>, first released with WinBoard 4.4 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. UCI2WB is open source, licensed under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPL Version 3</a>. As of 2018, <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> no longer contains <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a> and relies on the variant agnostic UCI2WB  <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Engines\">Engines</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Engines\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Category:UCI\" title=\"Category:UCI\">UCI Engines</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"GUIs\">GUIs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: GUIs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/XBoard\" title=\"XBoard\">XBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/InBetween\" title=\"InBetween\">InBetween</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/USI\" title=\"USI\">USI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wb2UCI\" title=\"Wb2UCI\">Wb2UCI</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Pfister\">Pfister</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Pfister\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=215566\">UCI2Wb by Odd Gunnar Malin</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_Gemuh\" title=\"Matthias Gemuh\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 26, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=41982\">uci2wb</a> by Andrew, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 29, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=46124\">A workaround for an uci2wb bug?</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Volker_Pittlik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Volker Pittlik (page does not exist)\">Volker Pittlik</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 20, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=46414\">How to use the UCI2WB adapter</a> by by Telmo Escobar, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 09, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=46825\">Winboard + UCI2WB + Fruit</a> by <a href=\"/Fabien_Letouzey\" title=\"Fabien Letouzey\">Fabien Letouzey</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 11, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=46851\">Is it time for a new and improved UCI2WB adapter?</a> by <a href=\"/G%C3%BCnther_Simon\" title=\"Günther Simon\">Günther Simon</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 12, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=47003\">UCI2WB \"replacement\" project news</a> by <a href=\"/Fabien_Letouzey\" title=\"Fabien Letouzey\">Fabien Letouzey</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 23, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=411604\">Fruit + uci2wb under Linux</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Joshua_Shriver&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Joshua Shriver (page does not exist)\">Joshua Shriver</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2005</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Muller\">Muller</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Muller\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=19&amp;t=50387\">WinBoard 4.4 downloads</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 05, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35482\">USI2WB / UCI2WB release</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 01, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rybkaforum.net/cgi-bin/rybkaforum/topic_show.pl?tid=18385\">UCI2WB / USI2WB</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Rybka Forum</a>, October 01, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=19&amp;t=52967\">Shogi in Unix/Linux?</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Joshua_Pettus&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Joshua Pettus (page does not exist)\">Joshua Pettus</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 19, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Shogi\" title=\"Shogi\">Shogi</a>, <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66194&amp;start=6\">Re: Cannot download Polyglot or KingSlayer source code</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 01, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=KingSlayer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"KingSlayer (page does not exist)\">KingSlayer</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Polyglot&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Polyglot (page does not exist)\">Polyglot</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69203\">UCI2WB 4.0</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 09, 2018</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hgm.nubati.net/cgi-bin/gitweb.cgi?p=uci2wb.git;a=summary\">hgm.nubati.net Git - uci2wb.git/summary</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=UCI2WB&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=47003\">UCI2WB \"replacement\" project news</a> by <a href=\"/Fabien_Letouzey\" title=\"Fabien Letouzey\">Fabien Letouzey</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 23, 2004</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hgm.nubati.net/usi.html\">The Universal Shogi Interface (USI)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=19&amp;t=50387\">WinBoard 4.4 downloads</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 05, 2009</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66194&amp;start=6\">Re: Cannot download